{"tid":1508304,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國上月購逾91萬噸美國大豆　較去年同期增3倍","createTime":"2019-08-26T13:10:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T15:44:47.000Z","uid":141151,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f4366bf415f2ade7eb5bd15e00b86fe82faf3ea5","tid":1508304,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:10:07.000Z","msg":"中國上月購逾91萬噸美國大豆　較去年同期增3倍<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190826/bkn-20190826093355859-0826_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20190826%2Fbkn-20190826093355859-0826_00952_001.html&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsZugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=280c9e11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190826/bkn-20190826093355859-0826_00952_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n關稅戰升溫之際，中國國企仍持續訂購美國大豆。英國傳媒周日（25日）引述中國海關數據，指中國上月向美國購入逾91萬噸大豆，較去年同期增加3倍，數量亦較本年6月增加近50%。 <br />\n<br />\n數據顯示，中國去年7月向美國購入逾30.8萬噸大豆，上月則購入逾91.18萬噸，本年6月購入61.4萬噸。相反，中國上月向巴西的大豆採購量較去年同期下降8.9%，只有642萬噸，較6月的550萬噸有所回升。 <br />\n<br />\n全球大豆主要進口國之一的中國，去年7月向美國大豆加徵25%關稅，導致大豆入口實際陷入停頓，直至去年12月同意恢復入口，但兩國的貿易糾紛升級，令市場陷入進一步動盪。"},{"pid":"a24b1788fce438333ecd75ff8ca3700aaf8c742d","tid":1508304,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:13:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">【眾籌 Google 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aeNRkyU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aeNRkyU</a>"},{"pid":"21f5187d51e90331f2f0d248cbfa06d192634178","tid":1508304,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:28:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4B5ZOzj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4B5ZOzj.gif&h=0e4bb77e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsZugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=9abda5ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsZugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=f3bdf001\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsZugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=04bd1dc4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"cba737d10a5825041009127197a2600eb897d311","tid":1508304,"uid":167903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:34:52.000Z","msg":"有冇手足可以解釋下買咁多豆有咩用<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e541b466593006e7dde948424dad2002e48fc860","tid":1508304,"uid":65074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:35:58.000Z","msg":"下一步該怎樣走？<br />\n<br />\n不要過慮，表面上政府好像以逸待勞，但實情是我們多面的極限施壓已成氣候，習近平和黑天鵝比我們更心急如焚&mdash;&mdash;他們正想利用談判搞散抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n2018年大陸境內債券違約規模達到1200億元，而今年的規模，是5700億元。<br />\n<br />\n59間企業設立的中國民營投資集團，533億元存續債券今年到期。4月首份5億美元債券違約，中建行已硬啃代還3億；另一份5億美元債券，8月2日到期。中民投講到明：還唔到。<br />\n<br />\n今年首6個月，中國企業債務違約金額突破600億。7月15日一天之內有5份債券違約。<br />\n<br />\n7月22日，美國制裁中國神秘石油入口商珠海振戎（北狄改名都衰過人，話明係用來振興伊朗這個西戎）。兩伊戰爭期間，中國向伊朗賣軍火，就是通過這間公司以石油代支。現時進口量佔全國進口量約25%。<br />\n<br />\n2019年有719隻地產債券到期，需要償還的金額達4567億元。2019年至2021三年間，地產企業海外債券到期規模都在200億美元之上。<br />\n<br />\n7月，失業大軍年增超過500萬人。<br />\n<br />\n7月，返鄉潮達740萬人。<br />\n<br />\n7月，特朗普否決將蘋果產品剔出加徵25%關稅的中國貨清單。<br />\n<br />\n7月，惠普、DELL決定將30％筆電生產撤離中國。<br />\n<br />\n7月，山東近百間院校搞農民工「副學士課程」，免考文化試，資格卻與高校畢業生睇齊。<br />\n<br />\n7月，秋行軍蟲和關稅夾擊下，中國多年來首次向俄羅斯入口大豆。<br />\n<br />\n2019年8月7日，資金緊張的中國企業集團中國民生投資集團(China Minsheng Investment Group, 簡稱：中民投)表示，其債券持有人已同意延後一隻5億美元違約債券的到期日。<br />\n中民投在周二晚間提交給新加坡交易所的一份文件中稱，這批票面利率3.8%的3年期有擔保債券於8月2日到期。該公司稱，包括應計利息在內，這批債券的未償付金額為5.095億美元。<br />\n中民投表示，正在嘗試籌集資金並出售離岸資產，以償付債券持有人。<br />\n<br />\n9月，南韓三星將關閉最後一間惠州工廠。<br />\n美國對300億中國貨品徵10%關稅。<br />\n<br />\n10月26日，美國給予WTO的限期屆滿，WTO必須決定是否將中國、香港和澳門剔出發展中經濟體。<br />\n<br />\n全國心臟病藥脷底丸斷貨，由9蚊暴漲至150蚊一樽。<br />\n<br />\n邊個等得？邊個唔等得？<br />\n<br />\n今日，中美貿易談判在上海重啟，預料實質成果不大。<br />\n<br />\n香港是大陸的後花園，不妨再燒幾把火。<br />\n<br />\n你國家仲有冇糧出啊？"},{"pid":"abd86a47ee59af6023f9a0ec2836ad1de6f30efd","tid":1508304,"uid":294555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cba737d10a5825041009127197a2600eb897d311","tid":1508304,"uid":167903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:34:52.000Z","msg":"有冇手足可以解釋下買咁多豆有咩用<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:37:07.000Z","msg":"最普遍咪包括喂豬 榨油 做豆類製品之類嘅囉"},{"pid":"2a53446dd016cf4082546ed0208e81255fd4c687","tid":1508304,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cba737d10a5825041009127197a2600eb897d311","tid":1508304,"uid":167903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:34:52.000Z","msg":"有冇手足可以解釋下買咁多豆有咩用<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:37:12.000Z","msg":"做飼料, 鍊油<br />\n好多乳類製品都係佢發酵<br />\n豉油/醬呢d"},{"pid":"f52ca3e0c4f947900d87ddbaa35f91594e8d59ed","tid":1508304,"uid":103936,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cba737d10a5825041009127197a2600eb897d311","tid":1508304,"uid":167903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:34:52.000Z","msg":"有冇手足可以解釋下買咁多豆有咩用<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:38:22.000Z","msg":"事實上，大豆最有價值的並非豆製品本身，而是其副產品──便宜的豆油，以及搾完豆油後的副產品──豆粕。<br />\n<br />\n豆油的使用早已滲透至絕大部份加工食品當中，豆油供應一斷，或變貴，將如星火燎原一般蔓延至食品工業，事關豆油可是現有食品體系的基本組成部份。不過對中國來說，豆粕又顯得更為重要，豆粕是優質的蛋白質來源，作為食用牲畜的精飼料使用。經濟增長下，其實食用油需求的增長十分有限，而對中國這種高速發展的國家而言，肉類需求增長則更為明顯。豆粕價格和肉類價格變動密不可分。<br />\n<br />\nGoogle 下就有答案<br />\n我當做下好心copy and paste"},{"pid":"db6ff8a6a85814d0a85ca5e6927fa42a4e770608","tid":1508304,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:38:51.000Z","msg":"廢老：買哂美國鬼啲豆餓死佢地"},{"pid":"c0445b7364e0a1bffebb91379cc47d1d5e7117ad","tid":1508304,"uid":190858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:42:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[核彈文宣]828#ProtestToo集會全世界都要去 平權=反極權 將火源燒開去</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1508048/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1508048/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qBGBRCw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqBGBRCw.jpg&h=c9bbcd64&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"77266c0ccb73561e9f83ca9fbf5bfbd984d25ce0","tid":1508304,"uid":167903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f52ca3e0c4f947900d87ddbaa35f91594e8d59ed","tid":1508304,"uid":103936,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cba737d10a5825041009127197a2600eb897d311","tid":1508304,"uid":167903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:34:52.000Z","msg":"有冇手足可以解釋下買咁多豆有咩用<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:38:22.000Z","msg":"事實上，大豆最有價值的並非豆製品本身，而是其副產品──便宜的豆油，以及搾完豆油後的副產品──豆粕。<br />\n<br />\n豆油的使用早已滲透至絕大部份加工食品當中，豆油供應一斷，或變貴，將如星火燎原一般蔓延至食品工業，事關豆油可是現有食品體系的基本組成部份。不過對中國來說，豆粕又顯得更為重要，豆粕是優質的蛋白質來源，作為食用牲畜的精飼料使用。經濟增長下，其實食用油需求的增長十分有限，而對中國這種高速發展的國家而言，肉類需求增長則更為明顯。豆粕價格和肉類價格變動密不可分。<br />\n<br />\nGoogle 下就有答案<br />\n我當做下好心copy and paste"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:42:21.000Z","msg":"sorry做左伸手黨"},{"pid":"011d3dd639b8873bea3af6a96ee49f956900fa81","tid":1508304,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T15:43:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03c53d8c26f5c17819145a19cd0233eba256cfef","tid":1508304,"uid":215876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T15:44:47.000Z","msg":"佢啲豬都死q曬<br />\n有豆無用啦"}]}